HOTAI MOTOR CO said unconsolidated sales
in April rose 55.81% to NT$5,195,608,000 from NT$3,334,660,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales           5,195,608        3,334,660   
YOY%              55.81%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           29,576,738       30,409,797  
YOY%              -2.74% 
=================================================================
 